g.ns12:text: \\centering\nThe extended\\\\\nSIAM represents these\\\\\nexcursions by generating\\\\\nthe interactions $J$ and $U_b$\\\\\nacross and within the bath.\\\\\nThese interactions mimick\\\\\nthe effect of the impurity\\\\\nand bath self-energies,\\\\\nas seen from\\\\\nDMFT.
\\flushleft\nDMFT represents\\\\\nexcursions from a site into\\\\\nthe bath in the form of self-\\\\\nenergies, for the impurity\\\\\nas well as the bath.
